Color Hand Drawn

Color Hand Drawn is a decorative icon style. It is a color version of Hand Drawn style.

The inner decorative border is dashed by irregular spaces. So it works great for desktop or web applications and mobile app screens.

As well as Cute Color, Color, Cute Clipart, and Circle Bubbles icon packs, the images work well as clipart for presentations, infographics, card design, and educational projects.

Download free Color Hand Drawn icons in different themes for UI and graphic design. You can also edit the images you want right on the spot.

The free graphics are pixel-perfect to fit your design and are available in both PNG and vector.
